    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Printing from glass plates, using either intaglio or planographic methods, developed and popularized from 1974 on primarily by Harvey K. Littleton.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
